---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="O Futuro da Inteligência Artificial" 
	description="Aiatolah - O principal portal bilíngue sobre IA, Guerra dos Chips e Mercado de Tecnologia."
>
	<main class="container">
		<header class="header animate-fade-in delay-1">
			<div class="logo-container">
				<div class="logo-glow"></div>
				<h1 class="logo gradient-text">Aiatolah</h1>
			</div>
			<nav class="lang-switch">
				<a href="#" class="active" title="Português">🇧🇷</a>
				<a href="#" title="English">🇺🇸</a>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<section class="hero glass-panel animate-fade-in delay-2">
			<h2 class="gradient-text">O Eixo Geopolítico da Inteligência Artificial</h2>
			<p>
				Acompanhe as análises mais profundas sobre a Guerra dos Chips, 
				o mercado de semicondutores (Nvidia, TSMC) e as inovações que moldam o futuro.
			</p>
			
			<div class="action-buttons">
				<a href="#" class="btn-neon">Assine o Boletim</a>
				<a href="#" class="btn-outline">Explorar Análises</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="market-ticker animate-fade-in delay-3">
			<div class="glass-panel ticker-box">
				<h3>Nvidia (NVDA)</h3>
				<span class="price-up">▲ Monitoramento Ativo</span>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-panel ticker-box">
				<h3>Guerra dos Chips</h3>
				<span class="status">Radar Geopolítico</span>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 2rem 0;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.logo-container {
		position: relative;
	}

	.logo {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		letter-spacing: -1px;
	}

	.lang-switch a {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		margin-left: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		transition: color 0.3s;
	}

	.lang-switch a.active, .lang-switch a:hover {
		color: var(--accent-primary);
	}

	.hero {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.hero h2 {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.hero p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
	}

	.action-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.btn-outline {
		display: inline-block;
		color: var(--text-main);
		font-weight: 600;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.btn-outline:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent-secondary);
		background: rgba(112, 0, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.market-ticker {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.ticker-box {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.ticker-box h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.price-up {
		color: var(--accent-primary);
		font-weight: 800;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.status {
		color: var(--accent-secondary);
		font-weight: 800;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
		.action-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
	}
</style>
